text: "Love is Strange" is 1956 song by Mickey & Sylvia. Love Is Strange may also refer to: *Love Is Strange (film), 2014 French-American drama film directed by Ira Sachs *Love Is Strange (album), studio album by Kenny Rogers *Love Is Strange: En Vivo Con Tino, 2010 live album by Jackson Browne and David Lindley
